<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.6.5">
<l>vāḷāya kaṇpaṉippa meṉmulaikaḷ poṉṉarumpa</l>
<l>nāṇāḷum niṉṉiṉaintu naivēṟkō maṇṇaḷanta</l>
<l>tāḷāḷā taṇkuṭantai nakarāḷā varaiyeṭutta</l>
<l>tōḷāḷā veṉṟaṉakkōr tuṇaiyāḷa ṉākāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For me who languishes, thinking of you day after day,</l>
<l>As my sword-like eyes pour [tears] and as gold [pallor] arises</l>
<l rend="indent">on my soft breasts,</l>
<l>[You] whose feet measured the earth, [you] who rules</l>
<l rend="indent">the cool city of Kuṭantai,</l>
<l>[You] whose arm lifted the mountain, will you not be an aid to me?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
